msgstr "已禁用"

msgid "Operations"
msgstr "操作"

msgid "Switch to Side Route Mode"
msgstr "切换到旁路由模式"

msgid "Automatically detect network environment and switch to side route mode. The router will work as a bypass gateway."
msgstr "自动检测网络环境并切换到旁路由模式，路由器将作为旁路网关工作。"

msgid "Restore Normal Mode"
msgstr "恢复正常模式"

msgid "Restore to normal router mode from backup."
msgstr "从备份恢复到正常路由模式。"

msgid "Important Notes"
msgstr "重要提示"

msgid "Warning"
msgstr "警告"

msgid "Switching modes will cause network interruption for a few seconds"
msgstr "切换模式会导致网络中断几秒钟"

msgid "In side route mode, the DHCP server will be turned off"
msgstr "旁路由模式下，DHCP 服务器会被关闭"

msgid "Devices need to manually set the gateway to the router's IP to use side route"
msgstr "设备需要手动设置网关为路由器 IP 才能使用旁路由"

msgid "Or set the gateway in the main router's DHCP settings"
msgstr "或者在主路由的 DHCP 设置中指定网关"

msgid "Configuration is automatically backed up before switching, and can be restored if there are issues"
msgstr "切换前会自动备份配置，出问题可以恢复"

